meta.title: Qt Quick Application
meta.description: Creates a Qt Quick application that can have both QML and C++ code. You can build the application and deploy it to desktop, embedded,  and mobile target platforms.

meta.title: Qt Widgets Application
meta.description:
Creates a widget-based Qt application that contains a Qt Widgets Designer-based main window and C++ source and header files to implement the application logic.
Preselects a desktop Qt for building the application if available.
